Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.50,0:01:32.51,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Teach Me How to Play Shogi (Continued)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.72,0:01:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next I'll introduce the characteristics\Nof each type of cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.18,0:01:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Okay!\N- Yes, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.39,0:01:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Good responses.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.23,0:01:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Welcome to Shogi Land
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.40,0:01:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Pawn
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.11,0:01:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pawn!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.53,0:01:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's a hard worker who moves ahead\None step at a time-meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.11,0:01:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I may be the weakest piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.11,0:02:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}My meaty paw punch\Nwill knock you silly-meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.82,0:02:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but there are scenarios where you can't\Nwin without me, so I'm quite important-meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.74,0:02:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Lance
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.41,0:02:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lance!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.16,0:02:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's a single-minded fellow\Nwho's as straight as an arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.87,0:02:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go straight ahead as far as you like!\NBut I can't turn back-meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.87,0:02:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'm kind of maladroit...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Knight
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.05,0:02:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.92,0:02:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He can hop right and left!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.01,0:02:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Only I can jump over\Nthe heads of enemies and allies alike-meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.30,0:02:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I hop and then let loose\Na kangaroo punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.93,0:02:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Silver General
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.60,0:02:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Silver General!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.35,0:02:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A cool guy with a little bit of an attitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.85,0:02:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to cool attacks, I'm a star!\NI'm good for both offense and defense-meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.02,0:02:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}But I'm wide open from\Nthe back and sides-meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.27,0:02:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Gold General
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.82,0:02:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gold General!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.53,0:02:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The confident bodyguard\Nwho protects the king!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.95,0:02:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I like being near the king!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.28,0:02:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'm the honest cat\Nwho has nothing to hide-meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.74,0:02:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I love getting close to\Nand then capturing the enemy king, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.99,0:02:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Rook
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rook!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.87,0:02:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest warrior! A true hero-meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can fly both horizontally and vertically-meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm popular with men and women\Nof all ages-meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.71,0:02:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Bishop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.34,0:02:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bishop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:03:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A heavyweight missile who's\Neffective diagonally as far as the eye can see!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.09,0:03:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a lonely guy who's always risking his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.97,0:03:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just be careful, because when I'm attacking,\Nmy defense might be weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.68,0:03:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}King
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.18,0:03:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,King!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.15,0:03:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Without me, there won't even be a game.\NSo don't leave me alone-meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.44,0:03:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I get captured, the game's over-meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.40,0:03:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, treat me like royalty-meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Only the king\Ncan move in every direction? Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.53,0:03:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! After all, he's the king!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.58,0:03:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Swish
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.95,0:03:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But also when needed,\Nhe's a great fighter in his own right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.08,0:03:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Swish
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So each piece has its own personality!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.29,0:03:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. And moreover, the awesome thing\Nabout these Shogi Land Kitties
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.59,0:03:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,is that when they advance step by step\Nand finally reach the enemy camp...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Enemy Army
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.10,0:03:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just one more step\Nto the enemy's camp-meow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...they can transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I reached the enemy camp-meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.44,0:03:59.69,DefaultLow,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pawn > Promoted Pawn\N(has the same abilities as Gold!!)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.73,0:03:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Meowy! I got promoted-meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.78,0:03:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}- The same as gold! The same as gold!\N- Congratulations! Please take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.07,0:04:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.99,0:04:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn you, Nikaidou...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hahahaha
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Squeee\NSqueee
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.12,0:04:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But this book is pretty easy to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it published from?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no publisher information.\NNo bar code either...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And no price, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.84,0:04:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it looks pretty fancy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Written and Illustrated\Nby Harunobu Nikaidou
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.68,0:04:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.14,0:04:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,N-N-N-N-Nikaidou, don't tell me you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I wrote and drew it.\NYou noticed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.97,0:04:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Shine
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.43,0:04:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, really? That's amazing!\NI wish I could draw like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.43,0:04:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Wow! Wow! Wow! Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.53,0:04:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if my drawings\Nare easy to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.99,0:04:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master, this is wonderful! I'm touched!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.78,0:04:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. Actually, I've loved to draw\Never since I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to contribute\Nto the popularization of my hobby,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so, I even asked the Daitokyo Printing\NCompany to throw it together simply like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then distributed copies to relatives\Nat the Nikaidou Family New Year's party.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.18,0:05:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Th-Th-Th-Th-Th...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.60,0:05:11.93,DefaultLeftH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Deluxe edition\NWith Gold Leaf\NUV Processing\NCloth Back Cover\NSpin\NEndpapers\NEndsheets\NFlower pattern-bound spine\NTrans TUVC\NEmbossed
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:11.93,RightSignL2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Super Fancy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Throw it together?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.35,0:05:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just glad they were interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the best thing to do\Nis introduce the detailed rules as they go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This being the first day,\NI'm pleased with what we accomplished.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.12,0:05:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In general, we did a good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Clench
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.00,0:05:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is how you build the future,\Ntaking one small step at a time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.72,0:05:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, the station isn't this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.69,0:05:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How far do you intend to accompany me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.77,0:06:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How far? Your apartment, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.11,0:06:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.36,0:06:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course... not. Not, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.41,0:06:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I shy away\Nfrom sleeping over at my best friend's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.79,0:06:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But let's try to shy away!\NAnd I'm not your best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.33,0:06:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I do worry! And so should you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.51,0:06:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master Kiriyama, Master Harunobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.76,0:06:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry we're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And now, if you would...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.15,0:06:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Put that in front of the closet on the right side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.48,0:06:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Oh no no no no
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here are some late-night snacks,\Nand breakfast for both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.15,0:06:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't help being concerned about your\Napartment's lack of daily necessities, Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.99,0:06:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking this would be a good opportunity,\NI picked something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is an excellent bed\Nthat folds up into a couch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.34,0:07:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Use it, by all means!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.25,0:07:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I realize it came late,\Nbut this is my housewarming gift to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:12.35,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Teach Me How to Play Shogi
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.40,0:08:48.40,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Image
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.16,0:09:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.79,0:09:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It won't fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.12,0:09:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shogi Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.84,0:09:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you sighing about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.26,0:09:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Issa and Mr. Smith...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Nikaidou isn't with you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.73,0:09:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that reminds me. I saw the NHK Cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your match.\NAnd Nikaidou's passionate commentary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.23,0:09:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you take all those impassioned lines\Nand etch them in your heart, Kiriyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.15,0:09:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Friendship truly is a wonderful thing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, just thinking about it again\Npulls on the old heartstrings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.78,0:09:40.04,DefaultLeftH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't even have\Nthe energy\Nto deny it anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was at my teacher's birthday party\Nthe day it aired,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.71,0:09:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but we all watched the recording that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.04,0:09:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you really want to win, then persevere!\NDon't just attack, you have to defend!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.54,0:09:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Mr. Nikaidou...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is this?\NWater coming out of my eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.80,0:09:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no... I'm going to cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.55,0:09:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What a good kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, what's this?\NThis is what I hate about getting old.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.18,0:10:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It makes you all sentimental.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.52,0:10:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nikaidou! I can't believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.36,0:10:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, we had a room\Nfull of adults bawling like babies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.36,0:10:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Everybody Loves Nikaidou
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.24,0:10:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I heard after the broadcast, Nikaidou had\Na bout of anemia and couldn't get to his feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.03,0:10:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What, he did?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He must've used up a lot of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.16,0:10:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He really tried his hardest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right? And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.83,0:10:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right? Yeesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.21,0:10:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of annoying\Nsince not one bit of it reaches your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.22,0:10:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nikaidou has six wins. He's incredibly focused.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He'll probably get promoted this season.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, his head is probably filled with\Nthe thought of facing off against you in C1.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.52,0:10:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Kiriyama!\NDon't disappoint Nikaidou!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Three wins and three losses.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't hold my ground here, I'll just\Nslide down until I reach the point of demotion.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you get a demotion, it won't get erased unless\Nyou have more wins the following season.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.54,0:11:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you get demoted twice,\Nyou drop down one class.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.72,0:11:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The battle to paint over a loss is even more\Nexhausting than the battle to move forward.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.93,0:11:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I witnessed my adoptive father\Ngo through that seesawing struggle{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.40,0:11:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}under the same roof\Nfor years after he was downgraded from B1.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.69,0:11:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It permeated my body.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.87,0:11:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Take better care of your shogi,\Nand yourself! I'm begging you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where does Nikaidou's energy come from?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.67,0:11:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not like his body is particularly strong.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.26,0:11:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it that he doesn't doubt himself?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That passion,\Nalways driving him on tenaciously...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.22,0:12:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whenever I'm with him, I feel suffocated.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I gradually get disgusted with myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He did such a great job drawing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like Hina and Momo both had fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My meaty paw punch\Nwill knock you silly-meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.09,0:12:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, Momo. The kitty doesn't like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.43,0:12:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They even put copies\Nof the picture book on the fridge
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.85,0:12:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so they can remember the moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.56,0:12:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When Grampa saw that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.10,0:13:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're lucky. How often does anybody get\Nthe chance to be tutored by two professionals?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.53,0:13:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they'll become incredibly strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.32,0:13:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't let them beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.66,0:13:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just wish those two guys\Nwould teach me. Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.62,0:13:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's goin' on with today's world?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.83,0:13:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it seems like he's looking forward to\Nplaying shogi with his granddaughters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.21,0:13:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I think about it like that,\Nshogi really is marvelous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's been around for hundreds of years,\Nand even now,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.43,0:13:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,as long as you have the board\Nand pieces, you can enjoy it at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.85,0:13:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, once you learn how to play,\Nit doesn't matter whether
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you're an adult or a child.\NYou can have fun playing earnestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And for your whole life.\NWhat a wonderful game...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The kitty transformed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.11,0:13:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Akari's words prompted an image of my father\Nto cross my mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.33,0:13:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His body would rock back and forth gently,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with his arms folded\Nand his left hand on his cheek.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.67,0:13:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}It was a natural habit that would appear\Nwhenever he was focused.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:14:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}I enjoyed watching him when he was like that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I could only see it when I did my very best,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}after studying so much\Nthat it made my head spin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I wanted to see that habit,\Nso I desperately tried my best.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.68,0:14:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kind, considerate of the people\Naround him, always smiling...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.77,0:14:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I saw his true face,\Nstripped of all social niceties.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.53,0:14:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What would Dad say\Nif he could see me right now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How could I have forgotten?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.17,0:14:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I'm standing in the world of shogi\Nthat Dad longed for.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.14,0:14:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How? How could I have forgotten that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.02,0:14:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Something so important...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.84,0:15:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyouko...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:33.01,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Image
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Long time no see, Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.01,0:15:37.02,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Distant Thunder (Part 1)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.27,0:15:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I was little,\NI saw lightning in the middle of the day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.53,0:15:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was a fleeting gleam of light that seemed\Nto tumble like liquid silver across the blue sky.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That one moment captivated my heart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:15:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if that brilliance...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.17,0:16:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...did bring on driving rain afterwards.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You look well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you... here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why? What an odd thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.60,0:16:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it so strange for a big sister\Nto worry for her little brother and check on him
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.98,0:16:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,after he's begun living alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.28,0:16:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll walk you to the station. It's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.86,0:16:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're not going to let me in?\NAfter I've come all this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.91,0:16:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.04,0:16:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why? It's messy, for one...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.46,0:16:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine. Show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.92,0:16:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to show.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.96,0:16:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Poor excuses. Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.59,0:16:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If "there's nothing to show,"\Nit can't be "messy," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.18,0:16:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it. The last train is—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.30,0:16:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My feet are cold! I need to go to the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.31,0:17:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me spell it all out for you, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.57,0:17:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They've finally warmed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.32,0:17:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how old is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like a dump from the outside,\Nbut it's surprisingly clean inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.16,0:17:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's 26 years old.\NBut the landlord just had it renovated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was lucky for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.05,0:17:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hey, Rei, get me a towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So why did you choose this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.39,0:17:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you have\Nany connections here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I came here once for work.\NI liked it because of the big, beautiful river.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.36,0:17:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The river? What?\NI can't remember, were you a fan of rivers?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:18:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The river, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We lived under the same roof for ten years,\Nbut it's like I barely know anything about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.38,0:18:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this apartment is cold. Can't you fix that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The air conditioner is old,\Nso it doesn't work well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.18,0:18:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Fwoop
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.43,0:18:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go opening things!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.47,0:18:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what a brat. This is a fine feather futon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.64,0:18:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was a housewarming gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.31,0:18:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You must've just gotten it.\NIt doesn't smell like you yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, that's some view.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really the sixth floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.37,0:18:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It seems higher.\NIs it because the river is so low?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So this is where you've been living.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.51,0:18:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You looked for it by yourself,\Ndecided on it yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really are self-centered, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dad was feeling down afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How did you rent it? Who's your guarantor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.31,0:19:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chairman Jinguuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.65,0:19:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Figures. He has a soft spot for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.32,0:19:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyouko, the last train—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.37,0:19:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go back home...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.45,0:19:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to that house?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.16,0:19:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It would make Dad happier that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.75,0:19:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.09,0:19:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lend me a T-shirt. I'm sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.59,0:19:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you and Dad have a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.06,0:19:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. I mean, I haven't seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.31,0:19:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been home lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.02,0:19:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still with that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.87,0:20:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.29,0:20:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't leave a scar at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.67,0:20:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gotou isn't a sane guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.81,0:20:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's bad for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.14,0:20:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.69,0:20:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't get violent with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.77,0:20:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get violent? With me? No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.65,0:20:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if he did...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.15,0:20:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...do you think I would just take it quietly?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.82,0:20:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I would stab him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.49,0:20:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...in his sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.45,0:20:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And he would never wake up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.04,0:20:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'd go that far?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.13,0:20:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.13,0:20:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.38,0:21:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I truly love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.36,0:21:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.90,0:21:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you have a match today, don't you?\NThat decides your rank...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.99,0:21:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who's your opponent again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.20,0:21:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Mr. Matsunaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.41,0:21:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How old is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.17,0:21:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sixty-four? Sixty-five? What a fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.92,0:21:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He won't move to the free class\Neven after falling to C1,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.59,0:21:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and keeps sticking it out, desperately,\NI guess you could say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.22,0:21:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I saw him play against Dad once.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.72,0:21:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was like he was holding on for dear life.\NIt was depressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.44,0:21:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But not quitting, even after all of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.98,0:21:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He must really love shogi, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.40,0:22:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.07,0:22:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.49,0:22:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hear if Mr. Matsunaga is demoted from C1,\Nhe'll finally retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.66,0:22:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that a downer?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.12,0:22:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's like you're going over there\Nto strangle an old, senile dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.58,0:22:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.\NNobody wants to be the one to do the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.92,0:22:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It kind of makes you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.38,0:22:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that in a situation like this,\Nmaybe you're the type to throw the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.68,0:22:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're such a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.65,0:22:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As she left, the sun shone through her hair,\Nilluminating it for a moment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.24,0:22:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And that light eventually\Nbrought on a pounding rain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.04,0:23:00.04,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Distant Thunder (Part 1)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.01,0:24:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.01,0:24:35.31,EpNum,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 9
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.59,0:24:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shouichi Matsunaga... 7th-dan.\NSixty-five years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.60,0:24:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From Fukushima Prefecture.\NA professional shogi player for forty years.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.14,0:24:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forty years in this world...\NI wonder how he feels right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.57,0:24:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm beat, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.53,0:24:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.03,0:24:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss the next episode\Nof "March Comes in Like a Lion" either!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.87,0:24:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please get a copy of Harunobu Nikaidou's\N"Shogi for Beginners Picture Book".
